    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at Gradation 1 for this model risk level. CFD predictions of hemolysis index agree with experimental measurements within uncertainty bounds at all five operating points. The worst-case operating condition is correctly identified by the model. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied relative to the predicate device across all assessed operating conditions. The credibility assessment supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
